WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.651
To be effective, you must develop four interdependent facets of

00:00:04.651 --> 00:00:09.302
CQ. Metacognitive CQ is your mental capability to acquire and

00:00:09.302 --> 00:00:13.953
understand cultural knowledge, verifying assumptions. Cognitive CQ is your general

00:00:13.953 --> 00:00:18.604
knowledge base. Motivational CQ is your persistence in adapting. Behavioral

00:00:18.604 --> 00:00:23.255
CQ is your capability to exhibit appropriate actions.
